## Test Directory

```
test/
├── models/
│   ├── user_test.rb
│   └── article_test.rb
├── controllers/
│   ├── articles_controller_test.rb
│   └── comments_controller_test.rb
├── system/                    # Integration tests
│   ├── articles_test.rb
│   └── authentication_test.rb
├── jobs/
│   └── article_notification_job_test.rb
├── mailers/
│   └── article_mailer_test.rb
├── fixtures/                  # Test data
│   ├── users.yml
│   ├── articles.yml
│   └── comments.yml
├── test_helper.rb
└── application_system_test_case.rb
```

**Rules:**
- Mirror app structure in tests
- One test file per class
- Use fixtures for test data
